{"tid":888644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男叫應召妹紓壓　驚見「破百大隻馬」急PO網求救","createTime":"2018-11-04T02:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T03:57:13.000Z","uid":32511,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4993297b55845e5e83e2372b0d51c7f0012917f7","tid":888644,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEwWJD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEwWJD8.png&h=dd66524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本一名網友近日在推特上，分享朋友的難忘經驗，原來他的朋友興致勃勃地打電話叫了個應召妹，見到本人卻嚇了一大跳，因為對方竟是個體重105公斤的「巨型應召妹」，照片一出讓網友看傻眼！<br />\n <br />\n日本網友くうねるあそぶ近日在推特上PO文，透漏朋友近日一時興起，打電話叫了一位應召妹，想不到卻來了一個105公斤的應召妹，趕緊傳照片向他求救！照片中，可以看到該名傳播妹似乎已經脫光了，也讓網友對故事結局充滿好奇。<br />\n <br />\n貼文一出後，不少網友都猜兩人最終仍然發生關係，留言表示「我會為你祈禱的」、「這種情況不能換人嗎」、「這個噸位我吃不下去&hellip;」、「騎乘位時千萬要小心呀」，還有人貼了一張米其林的圖片，笑說「原來是米其林呀！」"},{"pid":"d9ffbe4e74a4968aa676bd463c6bf42783b70c92","tid":888644,"uid":200474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0f1285b6af1fdd4b85d8f0d9e40a9af2d53910","tid":888644,"uid":1067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"佢會咁直接講你知佢有105公斤？"},{"pid":"410a1c75c726b8f1676d4da5ab56518059d7bd3f","tid":888644,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"起來， 讓我們勇敢的扯起來"},{"pid":"c443c595ba13e69ca12932fd5b1af3deb382dda2","tid":888644,"uid":212246,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20151104/large/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20151104%2Flarge%2F2